    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "pockets of ease dont really change the fact that the core of it is broken. no matter what i do, the world is still gonna treat me like an outsider. i feel like im just running on a treadmill that's going way too fast and i can't ever step off. sometimes i just think... what if i didn't have to do this at all? what if i just stopped trying to fight for a place that clearly doesn't want me? it almost sounds like a relief to think about just letting go of the struggle entirely.",
