      "content": "When the core feels broken and the effort to connect feels impossible, the thought of letting go can feel like the only perceived relief. Please know that these intense feelings of wanting to stop are signals that you are in profound pain, not that you have to give up permanently. If these thoughts are persistent, reaching out immediately to a crisis line can provide you with confidential, non-judgmental human support right now. You deserve care while you are navigating this deep pain.",
